If you don't feel like roleplaying and only want to be a 'filler' entry that's fine too, so long as your entry is drawn by you I will accept it. A predetermined tribute (in this case whoever's in District 9 slot 2, or the 18th tribute if there aren't any swaps) is IT. If IT shares an event with someone else, they tag that player.
